    title: 'Market Research',
    description: 'In an era where information is power, staying at the forefront of your industry requires more than just knowledge - it demands strategic foresight. Our in-depth market research services are crafted to propel your business forward by decoding market dynamics, trends, and emerging opportunities. By harnessing comprehensive data analytics.'
  },
  {
    icon: 'üíº',
    title: 'Business Process',
    description: 'Unlock the full potential of your operations with our business process optimization expertise, designed to transcend conventional efficiency standards. We believe in reimagining the DNA of operational excellence, distributing team specialties in marketing, streamlining, and optimizing your business processes.'
  },
  {
    icon: 'üîÑ',
    title: 'Digital Transformation',
